  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AboutFragment
    Displays an about page with information.
    FavoriteWorkoutsFragment
    Displays favorited workouts.
    FreeingOurselvesDatabaseHelper
    Handles creation and opening of the app's database.
    FreeingOurselvesDatabaseUtilities
    Provides a simple interface to the database.
    HealthCareProviderFragment
    Displays a list of questions to ask Health Care providers and a way to save questions.
    HealthNotesFragment
    Displays a list of saved health care questions with a space for notes.
    HealthQuestionAdapter
    An adapter for the HealthCareProviderFragment.
    MainActivity
    The top-level activity for Freeing Ourselves.
    MapActivity
    Displays a map with resource locations marked.
    ResourceListFragment
    Displays resources.
    TestosteroneFragment
    Displays introductory information regarding testosterone.
    TestosteroneHealthOverviewFragment
    Displays health overview of hormone treatment.
    TestosteroneHolisticCareFragment
    Displays information regarding holistic care when on hormone treatment.
    TestosteroneSurgeryInfoFragment
    Displays information regarding gender affirmation surgeries.
    TopFragment
    The home page for the Freeing Ourselves app.
    WorkoutActivity
    Displays information about a selected workout.
    WorkoutFragment
    Displays a list of workouts.
    WorkoutIntroFragment
    Displays an introduction to the workouts.

Package edu.mills.freeingourselves Description

Implementation of the app Freeing Ourselves. Created for Mills CS 115: Mobile Application Development, Spring 2017.
